Class HDBOfficerRegistration

Object
HDBOfficerRegistration
public class HDBOfficerRegistration extends Object
Represents a registration request from an HDB Officer to join a BTO project. This class models the relationship between an HDB Officer and a BTO project during the registration process. It tracks the status of the registration request (pending, approved, or rejected) and stores information about both the officer and the project they wish to join.
Version:
1.0
Author:
BTOMS Team
